text.title: Jenna Marbles
text.summary: Jenna Nicole Mourey, better known as Jenna Marbles, is a very successful American YouTube personality, vlogger, comedian and actress, known for her videos "How To Trick People Into Thinking You're Good Looking" and "How To Avoid Talking To People You Don't Want To Talk To".
